Project title : CoinMarketcap Crypto Currency price filtering and conversion 

Project Description:

This repository consists of two tests related to UI side and API side of Cryptocurrency Prices comparison and their conversions.


Tools and Technologies :

JAVA
Selenium
Cucumber BDD framework
RestAssured API framework
Maven Project
Report - cucumber plugin

How to RUN test:

Under /src/test/java, we have a package named "runner".
In which we have file named "RunnerClass.java"
Run this file as "JUnit Test".

Report:

Test report can be found under "Reports" folder.  